fast. \n\n\u2022  Dash is not a valid response for this item. \n\nCoding Tips \n\n\u2022  \u201cMinimal human assistance\u201d applies when the helper is contributing less than 25% of the total effort required \n\nto complete the task. \n\n\u2022  Assistance may include any combination of verbal cueing, environmental set-up, and/or actual hands-on \n\nassistance. \n\nM1860: Ambulation/Locomotion", "type": "Document"}}